'''Apple Pencil'''是一個由[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]所設計的[[觸控筆|觸控筆]]系列产品，只能在[[iPad_Pro|iPad Pro]]、[[iPad_(第六代)|iPad (第六代)]]、[[iPad_(第八代)|iPad (第八代)]]和[[iPad_mini_(第五代)|iPad mini (第五代)]]等特定型號的[[iPad|iPad系列]][[平板電腦|平板電腦]]使用，不支援[[iPhone|iPhone]]、[[iPod_Touch|iPod Touch]]及其他廠牌的行動裝置<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://technews.tw/2018/03/28/2018-apple-education-event/ |title=蘋果 2018 教育發表會：新款 9.7 吋 iPad 2018支援 Apple Pencil，售價台幣 10,900 元起 |accessdate=2018-03-31 |archive-date=2018-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330221332/http://technews.tw/2018/03/28/2018-apple-education-event/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mashable20150911">{{Cite web|url = http://mashable.com/2015/09/11/apple-jobs-script/#T_AaPDgmPmkF|title = Apple is not following Jobs' script and that's OK|date = September 12, 2015|accessdate = September 15, 2015|website = Mashable|publisher = |last = Ulanoff|first = Lance|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150915000916/http://mashable.com/2015/09/11/apple-jobs-script/#T_AaPDgmPmkF|archivedate = 2015-09-15}}</ref>。Apple Pencil 在2015年9月9日的秋季產品發表會上首次公開，並於2015年11月開始發售<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.apple.com/apple-pencil/|title = iPad Pro - Apple Pencil - Apple|date = September 9, 2015|accessdate = September 10, 2015|website = Apple.com|publisher = Apple Inc.|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910045125/https://www.apple.com/apple-pencil/|archivedate = 2015-09-10}}</ref>。

