Apple Pencil以[[藍牙|藍牙]]和iPad Pro連線<ref name="mashable20150911"/>。擁有壓力感測及角度偵測系統<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&Sect2=HITOFF&d=PALL&p=1&u=%2Fnetahtml%2FPTO%2Fsrchnum.htm&r=1&f=G&l=50&s1=8,638,320.PN.&OS=PN/8,638,320&RS=PN/8,638,320|title = United States Patent: 8638320|date = |accessdate = September 10, 2015|website = Patent Full Text|publisher = |last = Harley|display-authors = etal|archive-date = 2015-09-26|archive-url = https://archive.today/20150926013306/http://patft.uspto.gov/netacgi/nph-Parser?Sect1=PTO1&Sect2=HITOFF&d=PALL&p=1&u=/netahtml/PTO/srchnum.htm&r=1&f=G&l=50&s1=8,638,320.PN.&OS=PN/8,638,320&RS=PN/8,638,320|dead-url = no}}</ref>，可以偵測力道，例如：利用筆壓下更深或更淺的筆觸由使用者的力道決定。使用Apple Pencil更能在使用時減少[[延遲|延遲]]並順暢的繪畫<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = http://www.theverge.com/2015/9/9/9298117/apple-pencil-stylus-ipad-pro-steve-jobs|title = Here's why Apple made the stylus that Steve Jobs hated: Styluses and screens have come a long way|date = September 9, 2015|accessdate = September 10, 2015|website = The Verge|publisher = The Verge|last = Statt|first = Nick|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910233337/http://www.theverge.com/2015/9/9/9298117/apple-pencil-stylus-ipad-pro-steve-jobs|archivedate = 2015年9月10日|deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

iPad air 4能夠同時使用Apple Pencil與手指，且可偵測避免手掌誤觸控，因此可像一般書寫或繪畫時，將手掌放置於螢幕上而無須懸空<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://mashable.com/2015/09/09/hands-on-ipad-pro-apple-pencil/|title = Hands on with iPad Pro and Apple Pencil: A huge tablet and an impressive tool|date = September 10, 2015|accessdate = September 11, 2015|website = Mashable.com|publisher = |last = Ulanoff|first = Lance|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150911000359/http://mashable.com/2015/09/09/hands-on-ipad-pro-apple-pencil/|archivedate = 2015年9月11日|deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://arstechnica.com/apple/2015/09/hands-on-with-the-ipad-pro-its-keyboard-and-its-pencil/|title = Hands-on with the iPad Pro, its keyboard, and its pencil|date = September 9, 2015|accessdate = September 11, 2015|website = ArsTechnica.com|publisher = ArsTechnica|last = Cunningham|first = Andrew|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910121450/http://arstechnica.com/apple/2015/09/hands-on-with-the-ipad-pro-its-keyboard-and-its-pencil/|archivedate = 2015年9月10日|deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

=== 第一代 ===
第一代Apple Pencil有一個可以拆卸的筆蓋。在筆蓋底下有一個[[Lightning接头|Lightning連接器]]，可以連接Lightning裝置進行充電<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.macplus.net/depeche-84872-ipad-pro-la-tablette-geante|title = Zoom sur l’iPad Pro... la tablette géante.|date = September 9, 2015|accessdate = September 10, 2015|website = MacPlus|publisher = |last = bpepermans|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910184648/http://www.macplus.net/depeche-84872-ipad-pro-la-tablette-geante|archivedate = 2015年9月10日|deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

=== 第二代 ===
2018年10月30日，蘋果公司宣布推出第二代Apple Pencil搭配[[iPad_air4#世代#第三代|第四代iPad Air 4]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/30/18023772/new-apple-pencil-2-2018-ipad-stylus-price-release-date|title=The new Apple Pencil 2 has gesture controls and charges wirelessly from the iPad Pro|work=The Verge|access-date=2018-11-02|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109040834/https://www.theverge.com/2018/10/30/18023772/new-apple-pencil-2-2018-ipad-stylus-price-release-date}}</ref>。此代Apple Pencil使用磁吸在iPad機身上，以[[無線充電|無線方式充電]]，不再內建Lightning連接器。

== 用途 ==
Apple Pencil是設計用來讓藝術家完成創作，它讓在iPad Pro上面的電子繪畫變的可能。不過，[[多點觸控|多點觸控]]還是iPad Pro的主要輸入功能。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://money.cnn.com/2015/09/10/technology/apple-pencil-stylus/index.html?section=money_technology|title = Artists cheer the new Apple Pencil stylus|date = September 10, 2015|accessdate = September 10, 2015|website = CNN.com|publisher = CNN Money|last = Pagliery|first = Jose|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910235406/http://money.cnn.com/2015/09/10/technology/apple-pencil-stylus/index.html?section=money_technology|archivedate = 2015年9月10日|deadurl = yes}}</ref> 在2015年9月的蘋果發表會，蘋果公司演示了透過Apple Pencil來在[[Adobe_Creative_Suite|Adobe Creative Suite]]裡的軟體裡作畫<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://money.cnn.com/2015/09/09/technology/apple-photoshop-woman/index.html?iid=EL|title = Apple criticized for Photoshopping smile on woman's face|date = |accessdate = September 10, 2015|website = CNN.com|publisher = CNN Money|last = King|first = Hope|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910232506/http://money.cnn.com/2015/09/09/technology/apple-photoshop-woman/index.html?iid=EL|archivedate = 2015年9月10日|deadurl = yes}}</ref> 以及在[[Microsoft_Office|Microsoft Office]]裡的的軟體加入文章註解。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.businessinsider.com/apple-announces-stylus-a-product-steve-jobs-hated-2015-9?r=UK&IR=T|title = Apple just announced a product that Steve Jobs famously hated|date = September 9, 2015|accessdate = September 15, 2015|website = Business Insider|publisher = |last = Price|first = Rob|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150915002904/http://www.businessinsider.com/apple-announces-stylus-a-product-steve-jobs-hated-2015-9?r=UK&IR=T|archivedate = 2015年9月15日|deadurl = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.slashgear.com/apple-pencil-for-ipad-pro-revealed-the-stylus-time-has-come-09403026/|title = Apple Pencil for iPad Pro revealed: The stylus’ time has come|date = September 9, 2015|accessdate = September 15, 2015|website = Slashgear|publisher = |last = Davies|first = Chris|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910064054/http://www.slashgear.com/apple-pencil-for-ipad-pro-revealed-the-stylus-time-has-come-09403026/|archivedate = 2015年9月10日|deadurl = yes}}</ref>

== 支援 ==
第一代 Apple Pencil 僅支援以下 iPad 機型，同時採用 Lightning 接口進行充電及配對：
* iPad Pro 12.9 吋 (第一代及第二代)
* iPad Pro 9.7 吋
* iPad Pro 10.5 吋
* iPad (第六代、第七代、第八代及第九代）
* iPad Air (第三代)
* iPad mini (第五代)

第二代 Apple Pencil 僅支援以下 iPad 機型，同時採用吸附式無線方式進行充電及配對：
* iPad Pro 12.9 吋 (第三代、及第四代、第五代)
* iPad Pro 11 吋（第一代、及第二代、第三代）
* iPad Air (第四代、第五代)
* iPad mini (第六代)

